{"tid":1386361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢律師同我講既委任證問題","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:06:53.000Z","uid":191573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4deaa654e80d3ca7ed5caea3567dfe01c8426bba","tid":1386361,"uid":191573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚訓覺發夢夢到個律師朋友一齊食飯啦，咁就問下佢關於委任證既問題！<br />\n<br />\n1. 散仔軍裝膊頭有冧巴（佢可以好快咁Show一show 就收埋）<br />\n<br />\n咁就記得影低膊頭冧巴喎大家<br />\n<br />\n2.  便衣同白衫就無野睇啦當然，係尼一刻就記得準備文房四寶叫隻狗擔撚住張證，炒低曬佢冧巴同個名，以作日後如有需要投訴之用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好俾狗show 一 show 就收埋"},{"pid":"6a9d304b2858a51bcf6d47a2798c3a86d19e2473","tid":1386361,"uid":108606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"個問題係佢地唔show喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔show證，唔show你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e681b5e89d7ce454ad83acd93ce1bb74b441eb","tid":1386361,"uid":191573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a9d304b2858a51bcf6d47a2798c3a86d19e2473","tid":1386361,"uid":108606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"個問題係佢地唔show喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔show證，唔show你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"咁尼樣就無計啦，<br />\n見今日地鐵站有隻狗女好撚串咁同市民講唔好撚影到佢張證，犯法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b60b9be606357d51972aec2935d4d9226c0e39","tid":1386361,"uid":16123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n佢地當正根本唔洗帶證<br />\n就算有律師在場<br />\n都係一兩個show <br />\n其他狗唔洗show<br />\n屌佢老味死黑警"},{"pid":"2c9ea1333fb352016d8d27df03693634623ef310","tid":1386361,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"你律師朋友都算離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}